title: Threshold (001 - 054 + Extras) (1998 - 2006) (Ori-DCP)
description:
Threshold (001 - 054 + Extras) (1998 - 2006) (Ori-DCP)


Avatar launches our very first monthly series! Threshold features several short stories in each issue from the finest independent creators in the industry! Issue one features several great stories including Snowman 1944 with Tommy trying to rescue Hanna before she goes on the date from Hell, with Hitler; the Furies stumble across a hideous plot by Pan; Fuzzy Dice, an all new property by Matthew Clark (of Wonder Woman and Top Cow's Felon fame); and Tales of the Cyberangels where Bill Maus introduces us to the most powerful Cyberangel yet! Don't miss out on what is sure to be THE outlet for great independeant creators!
